description: Summonosuppresive Activity tests on materials A7, A13, and A14, previously supplied by Lorillard, according to the preliminary protocol recommended in Dr. Mulligan's January 29, 1981 letter to Dr. H. J. Minnemeyer. The study is to be conducted in accordance with the October 17, 1980 formal agreement between Borriston and Lorillard. The fixed price for testing all three materials is $1,800, and the price includes protocol development and costing information. Protocols resulting from this study become the property of Lorillard.
